03C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐκλείδε̄ς\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐκλείδε̄ς\">ΕΥΚΛΕΙ[....]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001432_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-08\" src=\"ISic001432_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001432.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-08\" src=\"ISic001432-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001432_detail_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-08\" src=\"ISic001432_detail_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001432_detail.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-08\" src=\"ISic001432_detail-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Text of IGPalermo\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>\u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Whether the name was in the Doric form (Eukleidas) or not, cannot be determined. The name is that of one of the three founders (oikists) of Himera (Thucydides VI.5.1) and so would seem to attest to a cult of the founder(s) and a base/statue in his honour.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1971.0764 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1970 347-349 no.6 fig.17 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001359\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001359\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manni Piraino 1973 17 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000531\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">12\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 2017 37 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002329\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002329\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Deep square letters, epsilon with three equal bars, perpendicular, lambda of standard form, upsilon without tail (V).\u003C/p> Line 1  15-18  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[264,267,270,273,276,279,282,285],{"id":265,"html":266},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F66S4X3M\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F66S4X3M\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan c